2012-12-27 Kaveh Vahedpour <k.vahedipour@fz-juelich.de> (1.1)

	* Perfomance and vectorization improvements
	* Fourier operators pluggable
	* Variadic returns for SVD and EIG
	* Lots of new funtions on matrices (Phase unwrapping etc.)

2012-01-10 Kaveh Vahedpour <k.vahedipour@fz-juelich.de> (1.0)

	* Redesign of transport layer
	* Introduction of more flexible workspace
	* Aligned memory in all cases
	* OpenCL modality
	* MPI modality
	* Lots of new matrix functions (interpolations etc.)

2010-08-12 Kaveh Vahedipour <k.vahedipour@fz-juelich.de> (0.4)
	
	* ReconStrategy.h configured now with XML backend
	* RRSModule.idl removed obsolete labels and introduced config
	* ReconClient.h configures remote interface with XML
	* testclt.cpp reflects those changes
	* ReconContext.h loads modules dynamically with this version
	* ReconContext.cpp ditto
	* Loader.h introduced for the above
	* configure.ac checks now for -ldl

	
